---
import config from '../../site.json';
---
<section id="about" class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-12">
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="fade-in-up">
        <div class="bg-base-200 rounded-3xl aspect-[4/3] overflow-hidden border border-base-300/50">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555396273-367ea4eb4db5?w=800&h=600&fit=crop" alt="Flame Kitchen restaurant" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text -->
      <div class="fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        <span class="badge badge-outline border-accent text-accent text-xs tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Our Story</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-6">Born from the<br /><span class="text-accent">Flame</span></h2>
        <p class="text-base-content/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Flame Kitchen started as a food truck on the streets of Atlanta with one mission: bring real soul food to the people. No shortcuts, no compromises — just bold flavors rooted in tradition and perfected over open fire.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base-content/70 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          What began as a weekend pop-up became a movement. Today, we're still cooking with the same passion, the same recipes passed down through generations, and the same belief that good food brings people together.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-accent">5+</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-content/50">Years Cooking</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-accent">50K+</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-content/50">Plates Served</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-accent">4.8</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-base-content/50">Star Rating</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
